notes.title: Funding
notes.p: This research was funded by Johnson Cancer Research Center’s (JCRC) Innovative Research Award, KSU the Startup Research funds, and BRIEF research award, Division of Biology, KSU to GV, and the JCRC’s undergraduate Cancer Research Award to CH. We also thank the Kansas Idea Network of Biomedical Research Excellence (K-INBRE) for the CORE Facility support award (grant number P20 GM103418) to GV.
